prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon-style slice of pepperoni pizza, anthropomorphic with big googly eyes and a wide, cheesy grin, is dramatically leaning back as if singing opera. Musical notes and little hearts float out of its mouth. In the center, in a beautiful, readable, flowing handwritten cursive script, the text reads: "Hope your birthday is supreme!". The entire scene is a flat 2D watercolor painting, with soft, flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, subtle paper texture, and organic paint bleeds at the edges of the pizza crust and cheese.
